# String Methods

.upper()
Convert all lowercase characters in a string to upper case

.lower()
Convert all upper case characters in the string into lower case

.title()
Convert a string into "Title Case" where the first character of each word is upper case

.strip()
Remove leading and trailing characters from a string


# Concatenation
A process of combining two or more strings into a single larger string

# f-strings
Formatted String Literals. Enclose expressions within curly crackets {} to embed them directly in the string. 